name: Jimmy Dahlqvist
title: Principal Cloud Architect
bio: Jimmy a developer and architect with a great passion for the Cloud in general and AWS in particular. He has been working in tech since 2003 and transitioned into cloud and AWS in 2015, and has since then been a true AWS-evangelist, leading to him being recognised as AWS Serverless Hero. His greatest passion lies in serverless technologies, and he love to share his knowledge with others. When he's not writing about serverless, you will find Jimmy talking about his other passions, IoT and BBQ.
session_titles: Event-Driven and serverless in world of IoT
